---
import { AlertCircle, Lightbulb, CheckCircle2, Quote } from '@lucide/astro';
---

	<!-- Platform Story: Modern Bento Grid -->
	<section class="py-24 bg-white relative">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
			<div class="mb-16">
				<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
					The Platform Story
				</span>
				<h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
					Why we built Pressly.
				</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
				<!-- Left Column: The Vision/Quote -->
				<div class="lg:col-span-5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors duration-500">
					<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors duration-500"></div>
					
					<div class="relative z-10 mb-12">
						<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-8 text-primary group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-500">
							<Quote class="w-7 h-7" />
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug">
							"We realized that by building a digital bridge between households and local vendors, we could solve everyday frustrations while directly increasing the income of hard-working micro-entrepreneurs."
						</h3>
					</div>
					
					<div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-4">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg shadow-md shadow-primary/20">
							P
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Pressly Founding Team</p>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Surat, Gujarat</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Right Column: The 3 Phases -->
				<div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-6">
					<!-- Phase 1 -->
					<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
						<div class="shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-rose-50 border border-rose-100 text-rose-500 flex items-center justify-center">
							<AlertCircle class="w-7 h-7" />
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">The Broken System</h4>
							<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
								The local ironing industry has operated identically for decades. Verbal counts, scribbled paper receipts, and zero visibility into delivery times. Clothes get misplaced, and trust diminishes.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Phase 2 -->
					<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
						<div class="shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 text-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center">
							<Lightbulb class="w-7 h-7" />
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">The Realization</h4>
							<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
								We saw an opportunity to intervene. A digital bridge connecting the customer and vendor could completely eliminate counting disputes and bring predictability to an entirely unorganized sector.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Phase 3 -->
					<div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
						<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/20 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
						<div class="relative z-10 shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/20 border border-primary/30 text-primary flex items-center justify-center">
							<CheckCircle2 class="w-7 h-7" />
						</div>
						<div class="relative z-10">
							<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Solution</h4>
							<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
								Pressly formalizes the interaction. Doorstep counting and live tracking for the customer, powered by a smart digital dashboard for the vendor. A true win-win ecosystem.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
